WHEN I KISSED HER.

17:29.833 --> 17:32.133
THAT'S WHY I LIKE
DATING MEN.

17:32.167 --> 17:35.133
WE DON'T CARE ABOUT TALLER,
JUST BIGGER.

17:35.167 --> 17:37.033
[ CHUCKLES ]
ANYWAY...

17:37.067 --> 17:39.600
