NEXT!

18:13.533 --> 18:15.433
YOU'VE BEEN QUIET
FOR A WHILE, APRIL.

18:15.467 --> 18:18.100
MINE WAS SO BAD, I DON'T EVEN
LIKE TO CALL IT MY FIRST.

18:18.133 --> 18:20.167
