MY BROTHER'S FRIEND.

18:20.200 --> 18:23.933
HE WAS CUTE, BUT IT WAS OVER
BEFORE IT STARTED.

18:23.967 --> 18:25.800
OH, NO.
HE WAS A 2-PUMP CHUMP?

18:25.833 --> 18:27.767
