IF YOU WANTED ME
TO MAKE THIS A PRIORITY,

23:15.233 --> 23:16.900
ALL YOU HAD TO DO WAS ASK.

23:16.933 --> 23:19.100
COME ON.

23:19.133 --> 23:21.800
LET'S GET YOU HOME.

23:21.833 --> 23:25.767
BYE, EVERYBODY!
THANKS FOR HAVING US!

23:25.800 --> 23:27.667
Omar: REALLY.

23:27.700 --> 23:29.600
Val: GOOD NIGHT, EVERYONE.

23:29.633 --> 23:30.600
April: THANK YOU,
IT WAS GREAT.

23:30.633 --> 23:32.333
SAFE JOURNEY.

23:34.167 --> 23:35.700
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
AHH.

23:37.833 --> 23:40.633
THAT WAS A TRULY
LOVELY EVENING, VALERIE.

23:40.667 --> 23:43.267
NOW COMES THE FUN PART.

23:43.300 --> 23:46.167
WOW.

23:46.200 --> 23:48.400
NO WONDER YOU WOULDN'T
LET ANYONE IN HERE.
[ Whispers ] YEAH.

23:48.433 --> 23:50.800
I GET A LITTLE ENTHUSIASTIC
WHEN I COOK.

23:50.833 --> 23:52.233
I'LL SAY.

23:52.267 --> 23:54.167
SO, UH, HOW CAN I HELP?

23:54.200 --> 23:57.200
BY GOING OUT THERE
AND RELAXING.

23:57.233 --> 23:59.633
WATCH THE NEWS,
HAVE ANOTHER DRINK,

23:59.667 --> 24:03.333
AND I WILL COME JOIN YOU
WHEN I'M DONE.

24:08.633 --> 24:10.100
SORRY, SUGAR.
I'LL GET A BROOM.

24:10.133 --> 24:11.433
NO, I'LL GET IT!

24:11.467 --> 24:12.767
JUST GO OUT THERE AND WAIT

24:12.800 --> 24:15.700
LIKE I ASKED YOU TO
IN THE FIRST PLACE, PLEASE.

24:15.733 --> 24:17.133
JUST THOUGHT THIS PAN
WOULD BE EASIER TO CLEAN

24:17.167 --> 24:18.267
IF IT SOAKED A LITTLE.

24:19.800 --> 24:24.200
[ GLASS SHARDS CLATTER ]

24:33.133 --> 24:37.300
2-CARET, EMERALD CUT,
STANDARD SETTING.

24:37.333 --> 24:39.600
YES, 20, READY TO SHIP
BY FRIDAY.

24:39.633 --> 24:41.067
NO EXCUSES.
[ PHONE BEEPS ]

24:41.100 --> 24:44.133
SORRY THAT I COULDN'T JOIN YOU
IN THE SHOWER, BABE,

24:44.167 --> 24:46.600
BUT, UH, DUTY CALLED.

24:46.633 --> 24:51.600
OH. I UNDERSTAND ABOUT HAVING
TO TAKE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

24:51.633 --> 24:53.800
WELL, I'LL BE OUT IN A MINUTE,
AND THEN WE CAN, UH,

24:53.833 --> 24:57.033
HANDLE SOME BUSINESS
OF OUR OWN.

25:02.667 --> 25:03.867
[ GLASS THUDS ]

25:07.467 --> 25:10.667
[ SHOWER RUNNING ]

25:18.500 --> 25:19.600
"ASHLEE"?

25:21.900 --> 25:24.133
WHO IN THE HELL IS ASHLEE?

25:35.967 --> 25:37.467
I'M TIRED.

25:37.500 --> 25:38.967
CAN WE DO THIS ANOTHER TIME?

25:39.000 --> 25:40.200
I CAN WORK WITH TIRED.

25:40.233 --> 25:41.767
SERIOUS, BABE.

25:41.800 --> 25:43.133
ANOTHER TIME.

25:43.167 --> 25:45.800
ARE YOU SLEEPING
WITH OTHER GIRLS?

25:45.833 --> 25:47.667
WHAT?

25:47.700 --> 25:49.167
I'M INTO YOU AND ONLY YOU.

25:49.200 --> 25:50.433
THEN WHY DON'T YOU
WANT TO BE WITH ME?

25:50.467 --> 25:51.700
I DO. I JUST...

25:51.733 --> 25:55.200
[ SIGHS ]

25:55.233 --> 25:56.333
I CAN'T.

25:56.367 --> 25:58.700
I HAVE A LOW LIBIDO.

25:58.733 --> 26:00.600
WAIT, WHAT EXACTLY
DOES THAT MEAN?

26:00.633 --> 26:03.233
IT MEANS I HAVE A DIFFICULT
TIME GETTING AROUSED.

26:03.267 --> 26:05.300
I'VE BEEN TO SEVERAL DOCTORS

26:05.333 --> 26:06.600
AND I'VE TRIED
EVERY DRUG POSSIBLE,

26:06.633 --> 26:07.933
BUT THERE'S NO CURE FOR IT.

26:07.967 --> 26:09.467
NOT EVEN VIAGRA?

26:09.500 --> 26:11.000
NO, A LOT OF IT'S
PSYCHOLOGICAL.

26:11.033 --> 26:12.400
I'M IN THERAPY
TWICE A WEEK ABOUT IT.

26:12.433 --> 26:13.533
I'M SORRY.

26:13.567 --> 26:17.333
SO...IN GENERAL,

26:17.367 --> 26:20.233
HOW OFTEN DO NIGHTS
LIKE LAST WEEK HAPPEN?

26:20.267 --> 26:23.167
COULD HAPPEN EVERY DAY
OR EVERY COUPLE OF MONTHS.

26:23.200 --> 26:25.633
I NEVER KNOW UNTIL I KNOW.

26:25.667 --> 26:28.433
AND THEN NIGHTS
LIKE TONIGHT HAPPEN, TOO,

26:28.467 --> 26:32.967
WHERE I'M READY
AND THEN I'M JUST...NOT.

26:33.000 --> 26:36.233
RELATIONSHIPS ARE ABOUT
A LOT MORE THAN SEX, CHRISTINA.

26:49.333 --> 26:51.500
WHAT THE HELL, APRIL?

26:51.533 --> 26:53.100
ONE OF MO'NIQUE'S PRODUCERS
JUST TEXTED ME.

26:53.133 --> 26:55.733
THEY'RE INTERESTED IN
BOOKING YOU FOR HER SHOW.

26:55.767 --> 26:56.967
WHOA, THAT'S GREAT!

26:57.000 --> 26:59.367
WAIT, JUST A PERFORMANCE
OR FOR AN INTERVIEW, TOO?

26:59.400 --> 27:01.700
WELL, SINCE YOU'RE INTO
TRADING SEX FOR FAVORS,

27:01.733 --> 27:03.767
MAYBE YOU CAN GIVE MO'NIQUE
SOME COUCH TIME TO, UH,

27:03.800 --> 27:05.267
GET SOME COUCH TIME.

27:05.300 --> 27:06.667
ALL RIGHT, YO,
I'M SICK OF THIS.

27:06.700 --> 27:08.000
THIS IS THE BEST NIGHT
OF MY CAREER IN YEARS,

27:08.033 --> 27:09.967
AND YOU'RE BEING
A TOTAL BUZZKILL.

27:10.000 --> 27:11.833
SORRY. JUST CALLING IT
LIKE I SEE IT.

27:11.867 --> 27:13.600
YEAH, WELL, I'LL CALL IT
HOW I SEE IT.

27:13.633 --> 27:16.167
EVER SINCE WE KISSED,
YOU'VE BEEN ACTING ALL JEALOUS.

27:16.200 --> 27:17.567
NO, REED.
[ BOTTLE THUDS ]

27:17.600 --> 27:19.133
EVER SINCE YOU SLEPT
WITH THE DEEJAY

27:19.167 --> 27:21.133
AND UNDERMINED EVERYTHING THAT
I'VE BEEN DOING PROFESSIONALLY,

27:21.167 --> 27:22.400
I'VE BEEN PISSED.

27:22.433 --> 27:23.600
SOUNDS LIKE JEALOUSY TO ME.

27:23.633 --> 27:25.167
WELL, IT'S NOT.

27:25.200 --> 27:26.967
AND NOW YOU DON'T KNOW
IF SHE PLAYED YOUR RECORD

27:27.000 --> 27:29.300
BECAUSE SHE TRULY LIKED IT
OR SHE LIKED THE SEX.

27:29.333 --> 27:31.633
YOU WERE THE ONE THAT WAS ALL,
"AM I GOOD ENOUGH?

27:31.667 --> 27:33.933
DO PEOPLE LIKE ME?
I WANT RESPECT."

27:33.967 --> 27:35.367
AND WHAT IF WORD GETS OUT

27:35.400 --> 27:37.267
THAT YOU'LL SCREW ANY DEEJAY
FOR AIRPLAY?

27:37.300 --> 27:39.267
NOT ANY DEEJAY,
JUST THE FEMALES.

27:39.300 --> 27:41.267
DAMN IT, REED!
THIS ISN'T A JOKE!

27:41.300 --> 27:43.733
IT KIND OF IS, APRIL.
IN FACT, IT'S ABSURD.

27:43.767 --> 27:46.567
LOOK, AS LONG AS THE PRODUCT'S
GOOD, NOBODY CARES.

27:46.600 --> 27:48.233
AND JUST SO YOU KNOW,
DENISE IS SEXY,

27:48.267 --> 27:50.033
BUT SHE'S NOT MY TYPE.

27:50.067 --> 27:51.833
[ Mouth full ]
I LIKE MY WOMEN MEAN, BLONDE,

27:51.867 --> 27:53.733
AND EMOTIONALLY UNAVAILABLE.

27:53.767 --> 27:55.800
OH, SHUT UP! GOD!

27:55.833 --> 27:57.500
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

27:57.533 --> 27:59.267
ALL RIGHT, YOU KNOW,
MOVES LIKE THAT

27:59.300 --> 28:00.800
JUST TURN ME ON
EVEN MORE.

28:11.867 --> 28:13.333
YOU KNOW...

28:13.367 --> 28:14.967
I STOPPED MYSELF
FROM CALLING

28:15.000 --> 28:17.900
BECAUSE I FEEL BAD
FOR SNOOPING IN YOUR PHONE.

28:17.933 --> 28:20.233
BUT I HAVE TO KNOW.

28:20.267 --> 28:21.800
WHO IS ASHLEE?

28:21.833 --> 28:24.200
WHAT KIND OF "BUDDY" IS SHE?

28:24.233 --> 28:25.800
YOU WENT IN MY PHONE?

28:25.833 --> 28:27.867
I... [ EXHALES ]
OH, I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU.

28:27.900 --> 28:29.867
I-I THOUGHT THAT WE WERE
WAY BEYOND THAT.

28:29.900 --> 28:30.933
SO DID I. BUT YOU --

28:30.967 --> 28:31.967
IF YOU WANTED
TO KNOW SOMETHING,

28:32.000 --> 28:33.000
THEN WHY DIDN'T
YOU JUST ASK ME?

28:33.033 --> 28:34.867
I DID ASK.

28:34.900 --> 28:36.567
BUT YOU SIDESTEPPED
THE QUESTION,

28:36.600 --> 28:39.467
JUST LIKE YOU'RE DOING NOW.

28:39.500 --> 28:42.233
LOOK, I KNOW IT WAS WRONG
TO LOOK IN YOUR PHONE,

28:42.267 --> 28:43.367
BUT I'M HUMAN.

28:43.400 --> 28:45.900
AND YOU'RE NOT
BEING STRAIGHT WITH ME.

28:45.933 --> 28:50.100
SO ONCE AGAIN -- AND, MALCOLM,
PLEASE BE HONEST WITH ME --

28:50.133 --> 28:51.867
WHO IS ASHLEE?

28:54.433 --> 29:00.067
ASHLEE IS MY EX-WIFE.

29:00.100 --> 29:02.900
YOUR EX-WIFE?

29:02.933 --> 29:04.433
YOU HAVE AN EX-WIFE?

29:04.467 --> 29:07.233
WHEN EXACTLY
WAS SHE YOUR WIFE?

29:07.267 --> 29:09.133
WE'VE BEEN DIVORCED
FOR TWO YEARS.

29:09.167 --> 29:12.333
WE WERE MARRIED FOR FOUR,
AND I JUST DON'T TALK ABOUT IT

29:12.367 --> 29:13.933
BECAUSE IT ALWAYS
BRINGS UP QUESTIONS.

29:13.967 --> 29:16.667
MALCOLM, PLEASE.

29:27.867 --> 29:30.467
I WAS DIFFERENT BACK THEN.

29:30.500 --> 29:35.167
I WAS REALLY WILD
AND I...

29:35.200 --> 29:38.900
I WASN'T
A VERY GOOD HUSBAND.

29:38.933 --> 29:42.000
I CHEATED.

29:42.033 --> 29:44.067
REPEATEDLY.

29:44.100 --> 29:48.433
I BROKE ASHLEE'S HEART
SO MANY TIMES.

29:48.467 --> 29:51.000
I STILL FEEL BAD ABOUT
THE WAY THAT I TREATED HER.

29:51.033 --> 29:53.467
AND SO EVEN THOUGH
WE BARELY SPEAK,

29:53.500 --> 29:57.233
I FEEL OBLIGATED TO
WHENEVER SHE CALLS ME.

29:57.267 --> 30:00.633
BUT THIS IN NO WAY AFFECTS
HOW I FEEL ABOUT YOU.

30:00.667 --> 30:04.133
I WANNA BELIEVE YOU, REALLY.

30:04.167 --> 30:07.533
BUT WHAT YOU SAID
MAKES IT EVEN HARDER.

30:07.567 --> 30:08.767
WHY?

30:08.800 --> 30:12.433
HMM? WHY?

30:12.467 --> 30:14.933
I'M BEING HONEST.

30:14.967 --> 30:21.800
MY EX-BOYFRIEND SEAN
USED TO SAY THE SAME THINGS.

30:21.833 --> 30:28.633
HE LIED AND CHEATED ON ME
JUST LIKE YOU DID ASHLEE,

30:28.667 --> 30:32.533
SO I KNOW FIRSTHAND
WHAT YOU PUT HER THROUGH.

30:32.567 --> 30:39.833
AND I MADE IT A POINT NEVER
TO LET A MAN GET CLOSE AGAIN.

30:39.867 --> 30:41.300
UNTIL NOW.

30:41.333 --> 30:45.067
SO WHAT'S TO STOP YOU
FROM DOING TO ME

30:45.100 --> 30:46.933
WHAT YOU DID TO HER?

30:46.967 --> 30:47.967
ME.

30:48.000 --> 30:51.267
BABE, I'M GONNA STOP ME.

30:51.300 --> 30:55.433
I...AVOIDED COMMITMENT
FOR A LONG TIME, TOO,

30:55.467 --> 30:58.767
BECAUSE I NEVER WANTED
TO HURT ANYONE AGAIN.

30:58.800 --> 31:06.633
SO I AM SURE THAT I WILL
NEVER HURT YOU, KEISHA.

31:06.667 --> 31:08.567
NOT LIKE THAT.

31:11.333 --> 31:12.367
OKAY.

31:16.100 --> 31:18.733
THANK YOU FOR TELLING ME
THE TRUTH.

31:24.367 --> 31:26.333
AND THANK YOU,

31:26.367 --> 31:29.200
FOR TRUSTING ME.

31:29.233 --> 31:30.900
NOW...

31:30.933 --> 31:34.567
[ SIGHS ] CAN I TRUST YOU
TO STAY OUT MY PHONE?

31:34.600 --> 31:37.167
[ EXHALES ]

31:37.200 --> 31:39.700
YEAH.

31:39.733 --> 31:42.500
I SWEAR I'LL NEVER
TOUCH YOUR PHONE AGAIN,

31:42.533 --> 31:47.367
OR YOUR COMPUTER
OR YOUR iPad

31:47.400 --> 31:50.967
OR YOUR DVR OR ANY OTHER
PERSONAL DEVICE.

31:51.000 --> 31:52.500
ALTHOUGH, I THINK
YOU SHOULD DELETE

31:52.533 --> 31:56.100
THOSE 5,000 "LAW & ORDERS"
YOU GOT IN THERE.

31:56.133 --> 31:59.133
I MEAN, IT'S ON ALL THE TIME.

31:59.167 --> 32:00.167
EVERY DAY.

32:00.200 --> 32:01.300
I LOVE YOU.

32:01.333 --> 32:03.600
WAIT, REPEAT
WHAT YOU JUST SAID.

32:03.633 --> 32:04.967
HAPPILY.

32:05.000 --> 32:06.333
I LOVE YOU, KEISHA.

32:06.367 --> 32:09.133
NOW PLEASE CONTINUE
DOGGING ON MY DVR

32:09.167 --> 32:12.300
'CAUSE YOU'VE GOT THOSE
2,000 --
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

32:26.500 --> 32:28.667
WHAT HAVE WE GOTTEN
OURSELVES INTO?

32:39.000 --> 32:41.433
OKAY, I'M ALL YOURS.

32:41.467 --> 32:44.567
DO YOU WANNA WATCH A MOVIE?

32:44.600 --> 32:47.000
ALL RIGHT, I'M SORRY.

32:47.033 --> 32:49.433
IT'S JUST THAT...
I HAVE A SYSTEM.

32:49.467 --> 32:52.133
AND I'M USED TO DOING THINGS
A CERTAIN WAY.

32:52.167 --> 32:54.700
I LEARNED A LOT ABOUT YOU
TONIGHT, VALERIE.

32:54.733 --> 32:57.033
I WATCHED YOU SPEND
THE WHOLE EVENING

32:57.067 --> 32:59.367
TAKING CARE OF EVERYBODY
BUT YOURSELF.

32:59.400 --> 33:01.033
[ CHUCKLES ]
I WAS THE HOSTESS.

33:01.067 --> 33:02.233
THAT'S MY JOB.

33:02.267 --> 33:04.700
YEAH, BUT I REMEMBER THIS
BEING PLANNED

33:04.733 --> 33:06.567
AS A CASUAL DOUBLE DATE,

33:06.600 --> 33:09.300
NOT A FULL BLOWN
3-COURSE MEAL FOR 10.

33:09.333 --> 33:11.567
I TOLD YOU,
MY FRIENDS ASKED AND --

33:11.600 --> 33:14.433
YOU COULDN'T SAY NO.

33:14.467 --> 33:16.433
THAT'S MY POINT.

33:16.467 --> 33:17.900
SEE,
I THINK YOUR CERTAIN WAY

33:17.933 --> 33:20.233
IS ALWAYS TO TAKE CARE
OF EVERYONE ELSE.

33:20.267 --> 33:22.933
I GUESS I AM USED TO
BEING THE GIVER

33:22.967 --> 33:24.600
IN MY RELATIONSHIPS,

33:24.633 --> 33:27.300
ESPECIALLY IN MY LAST ONE
WITH QUINN.

33:27.333 --> 33:32.833
BUT IT'S NOT SOMETHING I MIND
SO IT'S NOT A PROBLEM.

33:32.867 --> 33:34.000
IS IT?

33:34.033 --> 33:36.467
ONLY...

33:36.500 --> 33:38.033
IF YOU DON'T LET OTHERS
EXPRESS THEMSELVES

33:38.067 --> 33:40.700
BY GIVING TO YOU.

33:40.733 --> 33:44.233
SO, WITH THAT IN MIND,

33:44.267 --> 33:47.333
HOW 'BOUT WE SKIP THE MOVIE?

33:47.367 --> 33:49.000
WOULDN'T YOU MUCH RATHER
TAKE A NICE BUBBLE BATH

33:49.033 --> 33:50.167
AND GO TO BED?

33:50.200 --> 33:53.867
THAT SOUNDS GREAT,
BUT I CAN DO THAT LATER.

33:56.767 --> 33:58.967
WE'RE STILL ON OUR DATE.

33:59.000 --> 34:01.867
SUGAR, YOU KNOW WHAT
I WANNA DO?

34:01.900 --> 34:04.567
I WANNA TAKE CARE OF YOU
FOR THE REST OF THE EVENING,

34:04.600 --> 34:10.600
BECAUSE YOU ARE BEAUTIFUL
AND SPECIAL AND YOU DESERVE IT.

34:10.633 --> 34:15.100
AND THERE IS NOTHING THAT
WOULD GIVE ME MORE PLEASURE.

34:15.133 --> 34:18.867
OKAY.

34:18.900 --> 34:21.433
I CAN GIVE YOU THAT.

34:29.933 --> 34:32.967
[ FUNKASONIK'S
"LIGHT OF YOUR LOVE" PLAYING ]

34:37.900 --> 34:42.133
* MMM

34:42.167 --> 34:45.567
* UH-HUH

34:45.600 --> 34:48.633
***

34:48.667 --> 34:55.300
* THE SUN BEAMS DOWN
FROM MY WINDOW *

34:55.333 --> 34:57.733
* AND I KNOW

34:57.767 --> 35:03.533
* THAT THIS IS THE LIGHT
OF YOUR LOVE *

35:03.567 --> 35:07.633
* I COULD FEEL YOUR HEART

35:07.667 --> 35:12.767
* WHEREVER YOU ARE

35:12.800 --> 35:17.167
* IT SURROUNDS ME NOW

35:17.200 --> 35:21.800
* THE LIGHT OF YOUR LOVE

35:21.833 --> 35:26.333
* IT FILLS MY HEART

35:26.367 --> 35:33.000
* OPENING THE HEAVENS ABOVE

35:33.033 --> 35:35.167
* THE LIGHT

35:35.200 --> 35:38.167
* THAT THIS

35:38.200 --> 35:41.867
* IS LOVE

35:41.900 --> 35:44.767
* YOUR LOVE

35:44.800 --> 35:45.933
[ SWITCH CLICKS ]

35:45.967 --> 35:50.467
* IT SURROUNDS ME NOW

35:50.500 --> 35:53.800
* THE LIGHT OF YOUR LOVE

35:53.833 --> 35:56.533
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

36:05.133 --> 36:06.333
[ SWITCH CLICKS ]

36:08.900 --> 36:10.100
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS ]

36:12.567 --> 36:14.267
HEY.

36:15.933 --> 36:17.467
COME BACK.

36:20.533 --> 36:22.267
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS ]

36:22.300 --> 36:23.667
[ CELL PHONE THUDS ]

36:29.933 --> 36:32.333
KEEP TAKING CARE OF ME,
PLEASE.

36:35.200 --> 36:39.200
* AND REACH SO FAR

36:39.233 --> 36:42.533
* BUT DON'T TOUCH ME

36:42.567 --> 36:45.033
* I BELIEVE

36:45.067 --> 36:50.633
* IN SO MUCH IN YOU AND ME

36:50.667 --> 36:54.833
* NOW I CAN SEE YOUR HEART

36:54.867 --> 37:00.300
* WHEREVER YOU ARE

37:00.333 --> 37:03.733
* IT SURROUNDS ME NOW

37:03.767 --> 37:07.500
* THE LIGHT OF YOUR LOVE

37:07.533 --> 37:10.367
* THE LIGHT, THE LIGHT

37:10.400 --> 37:14.200
* IN MY HEART

37:14.233 --> 37:18.833
* OPENING THE HEAVENS ABOVE

37:22.767 --> 37:24.033
GOOD MORNING!

37:24.067 --> 37:25.200
Keisha: MORNING.

37:29.167 --> 37:31.200
THANKS AGAIN FOR THE PARTY.

37:31.233 --> 37:32.433
TURNED OUT TO BE
QUITE A NIGHT.

37:34.133 --> 37:37.333
ASA FINALLY TOLD ME
THAT THE PROBLEM ISN'T ME.

37:37.367 --> 37:38.767
IT IS HIS LOW LIBIDO.

37:38.800 --> 37:40.233
OOH. THAT'S JUST SAD.

37:40.267 --> 37:44.100
HE WANTS US TO KEEP DATING,
BUT I HAVE TO TELL HIM I CAN'T.

37:44.133 --> 37:47.833
I MEAN, I REALLY LIKE HIM,
BUT RIGHT NOW I LIKE SEX MORE.

37:47.867 --> 37:50.100
[ LAUGHS ]
DEEP.

37:50.133 --> 37:51.433
ANYWAY, VAL,

37:51.467 --> 37:55.033
SORRY IF I GOT A LITTLE
OUT OF POCKET LAST NIGHT.

37:55.067 --> 37:57.933
"IF"? "A LITTLE"?
[ LAUGHS ]

37:57.967 --> 38:02.033
ANYWAY, VINCENT AND I
WOULD BOTH BE HONORED

38:02.067 --> 38:04.167
IF YOU EVER INVITE US
BACK TO YOUR PLACE FOR DINNER.

38:04.200 --> 38:08.333
SURE, BUT NEXT TIME,
IT'S GONNA BE POTLUCK.

38:08.367 --> 38:09.433
HEY.
HI.

38:09.467 --> 38:10.567
SORRY IT TOOK A MINUTE.

38:10.600 --> 38:12.667
THIS SHOULD COVER THE CLOTHES
FOR DENISE.

38:12.700 --> 38:15.367
AH. THANK YOU.

38:15.400 --> 38:20.233
SO...HOW'D IT GO WITH YOU
AND REED AT HOME LAST NIGHT?

38:20.267 --> 38:23.400
MMM, YEAH. ESPECIALLY
AFTER THAT KISS.

38:23.433 --> 38:25.600
UGH. YOU GUYS SAW THAT?

38:25.633 --> 38:28.367
OUR WINDOWS ARE MADE OF
THIS MAGICAL MATERIAL

38:28.400 --> 38:32.233
CALLED GLASS,
SO YEAH, UH-HUH, WE SAW.

38:32.267 --> 38:34.933
SO, WHAT'S UP?

38:34.967 --> 38:36.600
WHAT'S UP IS REED
IS A SELF-INDULGENT

38:36.633 --> 38:38.667
WHORE OF A MUSICIAN
WHO SLEPT WITH THAT DEEJAY.

38:38.700 --> 38:40.467
AND I HATE THAT
HE'S SEXY TO ME.

38:40.500 --> 38:42.800
THOSE ARE ALWAYS
THE WORST ONES.

38:42.833 --> 38:44.533
BUT, HEY, I SAY
IF YOU WANT HIM,

38:44.567 --> 38:46.633
YOU SHOULD GO FOR IT.

38:46.667 --> 38:48.700
THAT'S KIND OF OPTIMISTIC
COMING FROM YOU.

38:48.733 --> 38:51.300
WELL, AFTER MALCOLM OPENED UP
ABOUT HAVING AN EX-WIFE,

38:51.333 --> 38:53.567
I HAVE REASON
TO BE OPTIMISTIC.

38:53.600 --> 38:55.467
HE WAS MARRIED?

38:55.500 --> 38:56.900
THAT'S NOT WHAT'S IMPORTANT.

38:56.933 --> 38:59.967
MALCOLM SAID THE "L" WORD TO ME,
AND I SAID IT BACK.

39:00.000 --> 39:03.033
AND NO, IT WASN'T
"LIQUID ASSETS."

39:03.067 --> 39:04.433
WAIT A MINUTE.

39:04.467 --> 39:07.000
KEISHA "AIN'T NOTHING GOING ON
BUT THE RENT" GREENE

39:07.033 --> 39:08.933
SAID THE "L" WORD AND MEANT IT?

39:08.967 --> 39:10.600
HELL, I'LL SAY IT NOW.

39:10.633 --> 39:12.367
MY NAME IS KEISHA GREENE

39:12.400 --> 39:15.167
AND I LOVES ME
SOME MALCOLM FRANKS.

39:15.200 --> 39:17.467
THAT'S RIGHT. LOVES.

39:17.500 --> 39:20.467
DAMN. I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D SEE THE DAY.

39:20.500 --> 39:22.367
GUESS THERE IS HOPE
FOR GAY MARRIAGE.

39:22.400 --> 39:24.433
I NEED AN OVERRIDE.

39:24.467 --> 39:27.967
WELL, I HAVE
SOME POST-PARTY NEWS AS WELL.

39:28.000 --> 39:29.633
YOU FINALLY SLEPT
WITH JERRY.

39:29.667 --> 39:31.233
[ GASPS ] HOW DID YOU KNOW?

39:31.267 --> 39:32.733
PLEASE.

39:32.767 --> 39:34.967
YOU'RE GLOWING SO MUCH I CAN
WAVE YOU AROUND AT A CONCERT.

39:35.000 --> 39:36.233
Val: [ LAUGHS ]

39:36.267 --> 39:37.833
SO, WAS IT GOOD?

39:37.867 --> 39:39.633
IT WAS...OH.

39:39.667 --> 39:42.300
HE WAS...OHH.

39:42.333 --> 39:43.567
THERE ARE NO WORDS.

39:43.600 --> 39:45.767
GO, JERRY.
DAMN.

39:45.800 --> 39:51.700
I'VE NEVER FELT SO WARM
OR SAFE OR SPECIAL.

39:51.733 --> 39:54.300
AND HAD ALL OF MY NEEDS --

39:54.333 --> 39:59.200
AND I MEAN ALL OF THEM --
MET SO INCREDIBLY WELL.

39:59.233 --> 40:01.733
I THINK I'M FALLING IN LOVE.

40:01.767 --> 40:04.667
AW.
I AM SO HAPPY
YOU'RE SO HAPPY.

40:04.700 --> 40:06.333
IF I DIDN'T LIKE
JERRY BEFORE,

40:06.367 --> 40:09.467
HE'S ONE OF
MY FAVORITE PEOPLE NOW.
AW.

40:09.500 --> 40:11.867
WELL, I'M REALLY GLAD
I GOT TO KNOW

40:11.900 --> 40:13.667
MALCOLM BETTER
LAST NIGHT, TOO.

40:13.700 --> 40:16.767
HE IS CLEARLY BRINGING OUT
THE BEST IN YOU.

40:16.800 --> 40:18.800
AND I'M SO GLAD
HE'S MAKING YOU SO HAPPY.

40:18.833 --> 40:21.267
AW, LOOK AT YOU GUYS.

40:21.300 --> 40:23.200
SOUNDS LIKE
YOU FINALLY FOUND THE ONES.

40:23.233 --> 40:24.667
YOU THINK?

40:24.700 --> 40:26.767
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE.

40:26.800 --> 40:31.833
WHO KNOWS? THIS TIME NEXT YEAR,
YOU TWO, WELL...

40:31.867 --> 40:34.400
LET'S JUST SAY YOU MAY NO LONGER
BE SINGLE LADIES.

40:34.433 --> 40:39.133
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:39.167 --> 40:40.133
BUT DON'T JINX IT.

40:40.167 --> 40:43.200
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:46.200 --> 40:47.467
NEXT ON "SINGLE LADIES"...

40:47.500 --> 40:49.967
WE NEED TO BUY A COUNTRY
AND MAKE YOU ITS QUEEN.

40:50.000 --> 40:51.633
DO YOU WANT ME
TO FINISH HIS ALBUM

40:51.667 --> 40:53.167
OR GET HIM
TO SIGN A NEW DEAL?

40:53.200 --> 40:54.500
I WANT YOU TO DO BOTH,

40:54.533 --> 40:57.633
AND I WANT YOU TO DO IT
WITH AS LITTLE LIP AS POSSIBLE.

40:57.667 --> 40:59.033
WHO DOES HE THINK I AM?
SOME CLUELESS KID

40:59.067 --> 41:00.700
POSTING SONGS ON YouTube?

41:01.933 --> 41:04.633
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

41:04.667 --> 41:05.833
WATCH YOUR BACK WITH HIM.

41:05.867 --> 41:07.700
EVERYTHING AIN'T
WHAT IT SEEMS.

41:07.733 --> 41:10.367
WHAT WAS ALL
THE WHISPER-WHISPER SIGH ABOUT?

41:10.400 --> 41:11.800
ME AND GABE ARE GONNA
HAVE A THREESOME.

41:12.900 --> 41:16.300
* FEELS SO FREE,
DON'T NEED ANYONE TO KEEP *

41:16.333 --> 41:19.867
* MY MIND, MY BODY, MY SOUL

41:19.900 --> 41:24.900
* SINGLE

41:24.933 --> 41:27.833
* LADIES
